Until today I benefit from contacts I have obtained through competitions.
The sale under franchise of his hotel helped Lukas Pytloun for the place of winner of the contest for the best Individual Entrepreneur.
The winner of the Best Individual Entrepreneur competition for the past year was Lukas Pytloun, a 28-year-old entrepreneur.
