This is also the view of Ms. Angelika Hilbeck.
This scientist has been conducting research in the field of genetics since 1994 and currently works at the Zurich University of Technology.
In this region, as in the United States, and now also in Europe, the industry sector is increasingly trying to influence or discredit critical scientists.
This is why there are hardly any researchers who are not linked to companies.
In the opinion of the companies, critical studies would not be published.
Hilbeck says "industry controls safety research."
