For Washington, which tracks Iranian clandestine networks for the acquisition of equipment for the nuclear program, the release of Majid Khakavand is bad news.
Did the France agree to a bargain?
The release of the Iranian against that of the French?
During a new interview with Kathleen Allegrone, on September 4, François Richier assures that this is not the case.
